cs.NE, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.DS, cs.SE

This paper proposes a multi-tasking optimization algorithm based on evolutionary computation, which is a subfield of machine learning and optimization. Therefore, cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) is the most likely sub-category. The algorithm also involves knowledge transfer and population distribution, which are related to topics in machine learning such as transfer learning and clustering, suggesting that cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) are also likely sub-categories. The algorithm also involves optimization and search, which are related to topics in computer science such as optimization and algorithms, suggesting that cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) and cs.SE (Software Engineering) are also possible sub-categories.
